      <p>hi </>one way of disposing off ur whole spices is to use them in a tea bag kinda arrangement. You can fashion one out of a couple of layers of cheesecloth or fine muslin, if u have access to it. After ur done cooking , just fish the tea bag out and voila. You get the flavors without the spice 😛</p>
