      <p>Hi,<br />Lovely recipe. Just a quick tip, cumin seeds are normally the first ones to go into the pan&#8230;pretty standard in Indian cooking. From my understanding, this is because of the fragrance that emanates when you let the seeds pop in the oil.</p>
