I am falling in love with your books and your recipes. I tried making this recipe last weekend, I loved the technique of adding water and reducing it, over and over. I cooked the onions until they were almost burnt, avoiding the carbon. My version fell flat.  What type of tomatoes/spices do you use? It is possible my spices were closer to pencil shavings.</p>
<p>Thank you for your time. Can&#8217;t wait for your new book. </p>
